        void applySecondaryTableReferences(TableReference tableReference,
                                   JoinType joinType,
                                   TableReferenceJoinPredicateProducer predicateProducer)
        Collect a table reference as part of the TableGroup.
        Parameters:
        tableReference - The TableReference.
        joinType - The type of join indicated by the mapping of the table, if it is to be joined
        predicateProducer - Function for creating the join predicate, if it is to be joined. The first argument passed to the function is the LHS reference. The second is the same as `tableReference`. The result is a SQL AST Predicate to use as the join-predicate
